findings.title: Liquidity adding
findings.description: The function _swapAndAddLp() adds liquidity with different proportion of tokens and requires rechecking of logic.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: ADMIN_ROLE has excessive privileges to launch token, change _rewardAddress, enable/disable _swapAndLiquifyEnabled, and change _contractRestriction.
